Now, by taking some values from the **share acquisition offer**, we know that the cost of $T$ is determined by the following equation:

$$
\begin{equation}
\text{Cost }_T=\text{Outstanding shares }_{T}\times\text{Exchange ratio}\times\text{price per share}_{BT}
\end{equation}
$$

Where,

$\text{Outstanding shares }_{T}=1,200$ and;

$\text{price per share}_{BT}=\$44.3559$
